@DATABASE "Kwik Snax"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - K - Kwik Snax"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - K
                   ====================================

                                 Kwik Snax
                                 =========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(46562,183)"}         46562,183
@{"Lives = x      " rxs "address command zxampoke(40905,255)"}         40905,x (x= 1-255)
@{"See End Of Game" rxs "address command zxampoke(40909,0)"}         40909,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
